{"id":94419,"date":"2019-01-29T14:35:27","date_gmt":"2019-01-29T14:35:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/?p=94419"},"modified":"2019-01-29T14:35:27","modified_gmt":"2019-01-29T14:35:27","slug":"financial-commission-participated-in-2019-ifx-expo-asia-in-hong-kong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/2019\/01\/29\/financial-commission-participated-in-2019-ifx-expo-asia-in-hong-kong\/","title":{"rendered":"Financial Commission Participated in 2019 IFX EXPO Asia in Hong Kong","gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"text"}]},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">January 29th, 2019: The Financial Commission today announces successful participation as an exhibitor at the 2019 IFX EXPO Asia, which took place January 22-24 at the Hong Kong Convention Center. Distinguished broker members and interested parties met with representatives to discuss Financial Commission\u2019s services for FX and digital asset trading providers.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02.jpg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-94447 size-400\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02-400x459.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"459\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02-400x459.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02-262x300.jpg 262w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02-768x881.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02-893x1024.jpg 893w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02-200x229.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02-600x688.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02-800x918.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.25.02.jpg 1116w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\nIFX EXPO event in Hong Kong saw more than 2,500 attendees, 60+ industry professionals and over 100 confirmed exhibitors and representatives from hundreds of financial services providers starting from the biggest IBs to top-tier retail brokers, asset managers, technology leaders, banks, hedge funds, and regtech startups.<\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-94460 size-400\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30-400x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30-400x533.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30-200x267.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30-800x1067.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.31.30.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<td style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-94429 size-400\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-400x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-400x533.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-768x1024.jpg 768w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-830x1107.jpg 830w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-230x307.jpg 230w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-350x467.jpg 350w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-480x640.jpg 480w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-200x267.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14-800x1067.jpg 800w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.14.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Participation in the IFX EXPO Asia event supports the industry and provides market participants with the chance to learn more about the Financial Commission\u2019s new dispute resolution services for digital asset traders and investors. This includes the new Blockchain Association and Blockchain Expert Committee, which include a growing list of digital asset firms that are committed to upholding the highest standards of commercial honor and best business practices in the Crypto and Blockchain spaces.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.07.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-94438 size-400\" src=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.07-400x533.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.07-400x533.jpg 400w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.07-225x300.jpg 225w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.07-200x267.jpg 200w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.07-600x800.jpg 600w, https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/2019-01-29-17.18.07.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Commenting about the event participation, Financial Commission Chairman, Peter Tatarnikov said, \u201cWe are proud to have successfully attended the IFX EXPO and want to thank all our members and delegates at the event that showed support.\u201d<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cThe Financial Commission continues to improve and expand its business model with new services for FX broker members and an entirely new association to help protect digital asset traders and investors, as well as promote self-regulatory efforts for Blockchain firms. Given the feedback we have received, we feel there is a great necessity in the services we provide for our clients from the side of market participants.\u201d<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>About Financial Commission<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Founded in 2013, the Financial Commission is a leading independent member-driven external dispute resolution (EDR) organization for international online brokerages that participate in global foreign exchange (forex), derivatives, and CFD markets. Financial Commission provides efficient compliance solutions to its members, alongside its External Dispute Resolution (EDR) mechanism that serves as an effective channel for processing complaints from clients of member firms.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To find out how the Commission is expanding efforts into self-regulation and transparency for the digital currencies and Blockchain markets, please visit the<a href=\"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/blockchain-association\/\"> Blockchain Association page<\/a> of our website.<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>January 29th, 2019: The Financial Commission today announces successful participation as an exhibitor at the 2019 IFX EXPO Asia, which took place January 22-24 at the Hong Kong Convention Center. Distinguished broker members and interested parties met with representatives to discuss Financial Commission\u2019s services for FX and digital asset trading providers. &nbsp; &nbsp; IFX EXPO [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false,"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"rendered","format":"html"}]},"author":13,"featured_media":94429,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[14,12,15,16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-94419","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-commission-news","category-company-news-news-events","category-press-release","category-press-releases-news-events"],"acf":[],"gt_translate_keys":[{"key":"link","format":"url"}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/94419","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/financialcommission.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,